event_person_shout
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
event_person_shout

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
event_person_shout -  This method is generated when a shout is done by a player.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void event_person_shout(object thing,
string start,
string mess,
string lang,
int * co_ord,
int range)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^thing%^RESET%^ - the thing doing the shout
%^BOLD%^start%^RESET%^ - the start string to print
%^BOLD%^mess%^RESET%^ - the message to print
%^BOLD%^lang%^RESET%^ - the language the shout is in
%^BOLD%^co_ord%^RESET%^ - the co-ordinate of the shouter
%^BOLD%^range%^RESET%^ - the range of the shout

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is generated when a shout is done by a player.
.EP

